      "id": "tw-cards-buttons",
      "moduleId": "tailwind-components",
      "title": "Cards & Buttons",
      "order": 1,
      "difficulty": "beginner",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- Cards: `border rounded-lg p-6 shadow` + content inside\n- Buttons: `px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded hover:bg-blue-600`\n- Hover states: `hover:` prefix\n- Transitions: `transition-colors duration-200`\n\n---\n\n# Cards & Buttons in Tailwind\n\n## Building Cards\n\nCards are containers for related content. Here's a basic card:\n\n```html\n<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6\"\u003e\n  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\"\u003e\n    Card Title\n  </h3\u003e\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"\u003e\n    Card description goes here.\n  </p\u003e\n  <button class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-600\"\u003e\n    Learn More\n  </button\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Card with Image\n\n```html\n<div class=\"max-w-sm rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-white\"\u003e\n  <img\n    class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"\n    src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200\"\n    alt=\"Card image\"\n  />\n  <div class=\"px-6 py-4\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003eThe Coldest Sunset</div\u003e\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-base\"\u003e\n      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.\n    </p\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  <div class=\"px-6 pt-4 pb-2\"\u003e\n    <span class=\"inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2\">#photography</span\u003e\n    <span class=\"inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2\">#travel</span\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Horizontal Card\n\n```html\n<div class=\"max-w-md mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden md:max-w-2xl\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"md:flex\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"md:shrink-0\"\u003e\n      <img\n        class=\"h-48 w-full object-cover md:h-full md:w-48\"\n        src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300\"\n        alt=\"Modern building architecture\"\n      />\n    </div\u003e\n    <div class=\"p-8\"\u003e\n      <div class=\"uppercase tracking-wide text-sm text-indigo-500 font-semibold\">\n        Case study\n      </div\u003e\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"block mt-1 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-black hover:underline\"\u003e\n        Finding customers for your new business\n      </a\u003e\n      <p class=\"mt-2 text-slate-500\"\u003e\n        Getting a new business off the ground is a lot of hard work.\n      </p\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Building Buttons\n\n### Button Variants\n\n```html\n<!-- Primary Button -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Primary\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Secondary Button -->\n<button class=\"bg-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-400 text-gray-800 font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Secondary\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Success Button -->\n<button class=\"bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Success\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Danger Button -->\n<button class=\"bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Danger\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Outline Button -->\n<button class=\"bg-transparent hover:bg-blue-500 text-blue-700 font-semibold hover:text-white py-2 px-4 border border-blue-500 hover:border-transparent rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Outline\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Ghost Button -->\n<button class=\"text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold py-2 px-4 transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Ghost\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Button Sizes\n\n```html\n<!-- Small -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white text-sm font-bold py-1 px-3 rounded\"\u003e\n  Small\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Medium (default) -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded\"\u003e\n  Medium\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Large -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white text-lg font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded\"\u003e\n  Large\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Full width -->\n<button class=\"w-full bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded\"\u003e\n  Full Width\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Button with Icon\n\n```html\n<button class=\"flex items-center bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n    <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 4v16m8-8H4\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\n  </svg\u003e\n  Add Item\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n## Hover States and Transitions\n\n### Basic Hover\n```html\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded\"\u003e\n  Hover Me\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Smooth Transitions\n```html\n<!-- Transition colors only -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n  Smooth Color Change\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Transition all properties -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-lg text-white py-2 px-4 rounded transition-all duration-200\"\u003e\n  All Properties\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Transform on Hover\n```html\n<!-- Scale up on hover -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 hover:scale-105 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded transition-all duration-200\"\u003e\n  Scale Up\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Lift effect -->\n<button class=\"bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 py-2 px-4 rounded shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200\"\u003e\n  Lift Effect\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n```html\n<!-- Basic Card -->\n<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\"\u003e...\u003c/div\u003e\n\n<!-- Basic Button -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded transition\"\u003e...\u003c/button\u003e\n\n<!-- With Transition -->\nclass=\"transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105\"\n```\n\n**Remember:**\n- ✅ Use `transition-colors` for smooth color changes\n- ✅ Use `hover:` prefix for hover states\n- ✅ Use `duration-200` or `duration-300` for timing\n- ✅ Make buttons accessible with focus states\n- ❌ Don't forget hover states on interactive elements\n- ❌ Don't use `transition-all` if you only need color changes",
      "codeExample": "<!-- Card Example -->\n<div class=\"max-w-sm rounded overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-white\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"px-6 py-4\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003eCard Title</div\u003e\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-base\"\u003e\n      Some quick example text to build on the card title.\n    </p\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  <div class=\"px-6 pt-4 pb-2\"\u003e\n    <button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-200\"\u003e\n      Action\n    </button\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Button Variants -->\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 mt-4\"\u003e\n  <button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded\"\u003ePrimary</button\u003e\n  <button class=\"bg-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-400 text-gray-800 py-2 px-4 rounded\"\u003eSecondary</button\u003e\n  <button class=\"border border-blue-500 text-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-50 py-2 px-4 rounded\"\u003eOutline</button\u003e\n</div\u003e"
    },
    {
      "id": "tw-navigation",
      "moduleId": "tailwind-components",
      "title": "Navigation Bars",
      "order": 2,
      "difficulty": "intermediate",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- Flexbox for layout: `flex items-center justify-between`\n- Sticky nav: `sticky top-0 z-50`\n- Mobile hamburger with `hidden md:flex`\n- Active states with conditional classes\n\n---\n\n# Navigation Bars with Tailwind\n\n## Basic Navigation\n\n```html\n<nav class=\"bg-white shadow\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex justify-between h-16\"\u003e\n      <!-- Logo -->\n      <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n        <a href=\"/\" class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-800\"\u003e\n          YourLogo\n        </a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n      \n      <!-- Desktop Menu -->\n      <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8\"\u003e\n        <a href=\"/\" class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 px-3 py-2\"\u003e\n          Home\n        </a\u003e\n        <a href=\"/about\" class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 px-3 py-2\"\u003e\n          About\n        </a\u003e\n        <a href=\"/services\" class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 px-3 py-2\"\u003e\n          Services\n        </a\u003e\n        <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded\"\u003e\n          Contact\n        </a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n      \n      <!-- Mobile Menu Button -->\n      <div class=\"md:hidden flex items-center\"\u003e\n        <button class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 focus:outline-none\"\u003e\n          <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"\u003e\n            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\" /\u003e\n          </svg\u003e\n        </button\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n\n  <!-- Mobile Menu (hidden by default) -->\n  <div class=\"md:hidden hidden\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"px-2 pt-2 pb-3 space-y-1\"\u003e\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"block text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-md\"\u003e\n        Home\n      </a\u003e\n      <a href=\"/about\" class=\"block text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-md\"\u003e\n        About\n      </a\u003e\n      <a href=\"/services\" class=\"block text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-md\"\u003e\n        Services\n      </a\u003e\n      <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"block text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-md\"\u003e\n        Contact\n      </a\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</nav\u003e\n```\n\n## Sticky Navigation\n\n```html\n<nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white shadow-md\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center h-16\"\u003e\n      <!-- Logo -->\n      <a href=\"/\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600\"\u003e\n        Brand\n      </a\u003e\n      \n      <!-- Navigation Links -->\n      <div class=\"hidden md:flex space-x-8\"\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-700 hover:text-indigo-600 font-medium transition-colors\"\u003e\n          Features\n        </a\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-700 hover:text-indigo-600 font-medium transition-colors\"\u003e\n          Pricing\n        </a\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-700 hover:text-indigo-600 font-medium transition-colors\"\u003e\n          About\n        </a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n      \n      <!-- CTA Button -->\n      <div class=\"hidden md:block\"\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-6 rounded-full transition-colors\"\u003e\n          Get Started\n        </a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</nav\u003e\n```\n\n## Navigation with Dropdown\n\n```html\n<nav class=\"bg-gray-800\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"\u003e\n      <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"\u003e\n          <span class=\"text-white text-xl font-bold\"\u003eLogo</span\u003e\n        </div\u003e\n        <div class=\"hidden md:block\"\u003e\n          <div class=\"ml-10 flex items-baseline space-x-4\"\u003e\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium\"\u003e\n              Dashboard\n            </a\u003e\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-700 hover:text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium\"\u003e\n              Team\n            </a\u003e\n            \n            <!-- Dropdown -->\n            <div class=\"relative group\"\u003e\n              <button class=\"text-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-700 hover:text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium inline-flex items-center\"\u003e\n                Projects\n                <svg class=\"ml-1 h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n                  <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" /\u003e\n                </svg\u003e\n              </button\u003e\n              \n              <!-- Dropdown menu -->\n              <div class=\"absolute left-0 mt-2 w-48 rounded-md shadow-lg bg-white ring-1 ring-black ring-opacity-5 opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200\"\u003e\n                <div class=\"py-1\" role=\"menu\"\u003e\n                  <a href=\"#\" class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100\" role=\"menuitem\"\u003eProject 1</a\u003e\n                  <a href=\"#\" class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100\" role=\"menuitem\"\u003eProject 2</a\u003e\n                  <a href=\"#\" class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100\" role=\"menuitem\"\u003eProject 3</a\u003e\n                </div\u003e\n              </div\u003e\n            </div\u003e\n          </div\u003e\n        </div\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</nav\u003e\n```\n\n## Active States\n\n```html\n<nav class=\"bg-white shadow\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex space-x-8 h-16\"\u003e\n      <a\n        href=\"/\"\n        class=\"inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-200\"\n        :class=\"$page.url === '/' ? 'border-indigo-500 text-gray-900' : 'border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300'\"\n      \u003e\n        Home\n      </a\u003e\n      <a\n        href=\"/about\"\n        class=\"inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-200\"\n        :class=\"$page.url === '/about' ? 'border-indigo-500 text-gray-900' : 'border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300'\"\n      \u003e\n        About\n      </a\u003e\n      <a\n        href=\"/contact\"\n        class=\"inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-200\"\n        :class=\"$page.url === '/contact' ? 'border-indigo-500 text-gray-900' : 'border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300'\"\n      \u003e\n        Contact\n      </a\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</nav\u003e\n```\n\n## Breadcrumb Navigation\n\n```html\n<nav class=\"flex\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"\u003e\n  <ol class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-1 md:space-x-3\"\u003e\n    <li class=\"inline-flex items-center\"\u003e\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900\"\u003e\n        Home\n      </a\u003e\n    </li\u003e\n    <li\u003e\n      <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n        <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"\u003e\n          <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" /\u003e\n        </svg\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"ml-1 text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900 md:ml-2\"\u003e\n          Projects\n        </a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </li\u003e\n    <li aria-current=\"page\"\u003e\n      <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n        <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"\u003e\n          <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" /\u003e\n        </svg\u003e\n        <span class=\"ml-1 text-gray-500 md:ml-2\"\u003e\n          Project ABC\n        </span\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </li\u003e\n  </ol\u003e\n</nav\u003e\n```\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n```html\n<!-- Basic nav structure -->\n<nav class=\"bg-white shadow\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex justify-between h-16\"\u003e...\u003c/div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</nav\u003e\n\n<!-- Sticky nav -->\n<nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white shadow\"\u003e...\u003c/nav\u003e\n\n<!-- Hide on mobile, show on desktop -->\n<div class=\"hidden md:flex\"\u003e...\u003c/div\u003e\n```\n\n**Remember:**\n- ✅ Use `sticky top-0 z-50` for fixed navigation\n- ✅ Use `hidden md:flex` pattern for responsive nav\n- ✅ Always include mobile menu toggle\n- ✅ Use semantic HTML (`nav`, `ul`, `li`)\n- ✅ Include focus states for accessibility\n- ❌ Don't forget to test on mobile devices\n- ❌ Don't use `position: fixed` without considering content shift",
      "codeExample": "<nav class=\"bg-white shadow\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex justify-between h-16\"\u003e\n      <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n        <a href=\"/\" class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-800\"\u003eLogo</a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n      <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8\"\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900\"\u003eHome</a\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900\"\u003eAbout</a\u003e\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded\"\u003eContact</a\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</nav\u003e"
    },
    {
      "id": "tw-forms",
      "moduleId": "tailwind-components",
      "title": "Styled Forms",
      "order": 3,
      "difficulty": "intermediate",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- Input: `w-full px-3 py-2 border rounded focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500`\n- Label: `block text-sm font-bold mb-1`\n- Focus states: `focus:` prefix\n- Ring utility for focus outlines\n\n---\n\n# Styled Forms with Tailwind\n\n## Basic Form Structure\n\n```html\n<form class=\"max-w-lg mx-auto space-y-6\"\u003e\n  <!-- Email Field -->\n  <div\u003e\n    <label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003e\n      Email Address\n    </label\u003e\n    <input\n      type=\"email\"\n      id=\"email\"\n      name=\"email\"\n      class=\"w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500\"\n      placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n    />\n  </div\u003e\n  \n  <!-- Password Field -->\n  <div\u003e\n    <label for=\"password\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003e\n      Password\n    </label\u003e\n    <input\n      type=\"password\"\n      id=\"password\"\n      name=\"password\"\n      class=\"w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500\"\n      placeholder=\"••••••••\"\n    />\n  </div\u003e\n  \n  <!-- Submit Button -->\n  <button\n    type=\"submit\"\n    class=\"w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"\n  \u003e\n    Sign In\n  </button\u003e\n</form\u003e\n```\n\n## Input Types\n\n### Text Input with Icon\n\n```html\n<div class=\"relative\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none\"\u003e\n    <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n      <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z\" /\u003e\n    </svg\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  <input\n    type=\"text\"\n    class=\"block w-full pl-10 pr-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md leading-5 bg-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:placeholder-gray-400 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm\"\n    placeholder=\"Username\"\n  />\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Select Dropdown\n\n```html\n<div\u003e\n  <label for=\"country\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003e\n    Country\n  </label\u003e\n  <select\n    id=\"country\"\n    name=\"country\"\n    class=\"block w-full pl-3 pr-10 py-2 text-base border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm rounded-md\"\n  \u003e\n    <option value=\"\"\u003eSelect a country</option\u003e\n    <option value=\"us\"\u003eUnited States</option\u003e\n    <option value=\"ca\"\u003eCanada</option\u003e\n    <option value=\"mx\"\u003eMexico</option\u003e\n  </select\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Textarea\n\n```html\n<div\u003e\n  <label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003e\n    Message\n  </label\u003e\n  <textarea\n    id=\"message\"\n    name=\"message\"\n    rows=\"4\"\n    class=\"block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm\"\n    placeholder=\"Enter your message...\"\n  \u003e</textarea\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Checkbox\n\n```html\n<div class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"flex items-center h-5\"\u003e\n    <input\n      id=\"comments\"\n      name=\"comments\"\n      type=\"checkbox\"\n      class=\"focus:ring-blue-500 h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded\"\n    />\n  </div\u003e\n  <div class=\"ml-3 text-sm\"\u003e\n    <label for=\"comments\" class=\"font-medium text-gray-700\"\u003e\n      Comments\n    </label\u003e\n    <p class=\"text-gray-500\"\u003eGet notified when someones posts a comment on a posting.</p\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Radio Buttons\n\n```html\n<div class=\"space-y-4\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n    <input\n      id=\"push-everything\"\n      name=\"push-notifications\"\n      type=\"radio\"\n      class=\"focus:ring-blue-500 h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300\"\n    />\n    <label for=\"push-everything\" class=\"ml-3 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\"\u003e\n      Everything\n    </label\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  \n  <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n    <input\n      id=\"push-email\"\n      name=\"push-notifications\"\n      type=\"radio\"\n      class=\"focus:ring-blue-500 h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300\"\n    />\n    <label for=\"push-email\" class=\"ml-3 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\"\u003e\n      Same as email\n    </label\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Form Validation States\n\n```html\n<!-- Error State -->\n<div\u003e\n  <label for=\"email-error\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-red-700\"\u003e\n    Email\n  </label\u003e\n  <div class=\"mt-1 relative rounded-md shadow-sm\"\u003e\n    <input\n      type=\"email\"\n      name=\"email\"\n      id=\"email-error\"\n      class=\"block w-full pr-10 border-red-300 text-red-900 placeholder-red-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500 sm:text-sm rounded-md\"\n      placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n      value=\"invalid-email\"\n      aria-invalid=\"true\"\n      aria-describedby=\"email-error\"\n    />\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none\"\u003e\n      <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-red-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"\u003e\n        <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" /\u003e\n      </svg\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  <p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-red-600\" id=\"email-error\"\u003e\n    Please enter a valid email address.\n  </p\u003e\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Success State -->\n<div\u003e\n  <label for=\"email-success\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-green-700\"\u003e\n    Email\n  </label\u003e\n  <div class=\"mt-1 relative rounded-md shadow-sm\"\u003e\n    <input\n      type=\"email\"\n      name=\"email\"\n      id=\"email-success\"\n      class=\"block w-full pr-10 border-green-300 text-green-900 placeholder-green-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500 sm:text-sm rounded-md\"\n      placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n      value=\"valid@email.com\"\n    />\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none\"\u003e\n      <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-green-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"\u003e\n        <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" /\u003e\n      </svg\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  <p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-green-600\"\u003e\n    Email is valid!\n  </p\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Complete Login Form\n\n```html\n<div class=\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"max-w-md w-full space-y-8\"\u003e\n    <div\u003e\n      <h2 class=\"mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900\"\u003e\n        Sign in to your account\n      </h2\u003e\n      <p class=\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\"\u003e\n        Or\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-500\"\u003e\n          start your 14-day free trial\n        </a\u003e\n      </p\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n    <form class=\"mt-8 space-y-6\" action=\"#\" method=\"POST\"\u003e\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"remember\" value=\"true\" /\u003e\n      <div class=\"rounded-md shadow-sm -space-y-px\"\u003e\n        <div\u003e\n          <label for=\"email-address\" class=\"sr-only\"\u003eEmail address</label\u003e\n          <input\n            id=\"email-address\"\n            name=\"email\"\n            type=\"email\"\n            autocomplete=\"email\"\n            required\n            class=\"appearance-none rounded-none relative block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 placeholder-gray-500 text-gray-900 rounded-t-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 focus:z-10 sm:text-sm\"\n            placeholder=\"Email address\"\n          />\n        </div\u003e\n        <div\u003e\n          <label for=\"password\" class=\"sr-only\"\u003ePassword</label\u003e\n          <input\n            id=\"password\"\n            name=\"password\"\n            type=\"password\"\n            autocomplete=\"current-password\"\n            required\n            class=\"appearance-none rounded-none relative block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 placeholder-gray-500 text-gray-900 rounded-b-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 focus:z-10 sm:text-sm\"\n            placeholder=\"Password\"\n          />\n        </div\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"\u003e\n        <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n          <input\n            id=\"remember-me\"\n            name=\"remember-me\"\n            type=\"checkbox\"\n            class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded\"\n          />\n          <label for=\"remember-me\" class=\"ml-2 block text-sm text-gray-900\"\u003e\n            Remember me\n          </label\u003e\n        </div\u003e\n\n        <div class=\"text-sm\"\u003e\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-500\"\u003e\n            Forgot your password?\n          </a\u003e\n        </div\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n\n      <div\u003e\n        <button\n          type=\"submit\"\n          class=\"group relative w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"\n        \u003e\n          <span class=\"absolute left-0 inset-y-0 flex items-center pl-3\"\u003e\n            <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 group-hover:text-blue-400\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"\u003e\n              <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" /\u003e\n            </svg\u003e\n          </span\u003e\n          Sign in\n        </button\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </form\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n```html\n<!-- Basic input -->\n<input class=\"w-full px-3 py-2 border rounded focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none\" /\u003e\n\n<!-- Label -->\n<label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003eLabel</label\u003e\n\n<!-- Error state -->\n<input class=\"border-red-300 text-red-900 focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500\" /\u003e\n\n<!-- Checkbox -->\n<input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded\" /\u003e\n```\n\n**Remember:**\n- ✅ Use `focus:ring` for accessible focus states\n- ✅ Use `w-full` on inputs for responsive width\n- ✅ Include labels for all form fields\n- ✅ Use proper input types (email, tel, etc.)\n- ✅ Style error states with red colors\n- ❌ Don't remove focus outlines entirely\n- ❌ Don't forget placeholder text",
      "codeExample": "<form class=\"max-w-md mx-auto space-y-4\"\u003e\n  <div\u003e\n    <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003eEmail</label\u003e\n    <input\n      type=\"email\"\n      class=\"w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"\n      placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n    /\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  \n  <div\u003e\n    <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\"\u003ePassword</label\u003e\n    <input\n      type=\"password\"\n      class=\"w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\"\n      placeholder=\"••••••••\"\n    /\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  \n  <div class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded\" /\u003e\n    <label class=\"ml-2 text-sm text-gray-700\"\u003eRemember me</label\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n  \n  <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700\"\u003e\n    Sign In\n  </button\u003e\n</form\u003e"
