      "difficulty": "intermediate",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- `transition` enables smooth changes\n- `duration-200`, `duration-300` control speed\n- `hover:scale-105` for zoom effect\n- `animate-spin`, `animate-pulse`, `animate-bounce` built-in\n- `transform` utilities: `scale`, `rotate`, `translate`\n\n---\n\n# Transitions & Animations in Tailwind\n\n## Transitions\n\n### Basic Transition\n\nAdd smooth transitions between states:\n\n```html\n<!-- Color transition -->\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors duration-300\"\u003e\n  Hover Me\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Transition Properties\n\n```html\n<!-- Transition colors only -->\n<button class=\"transition-colors duration-300\"\u003eColors</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Transition background only -->\n<button class=\"transition-bg duration-300\"\u003eBackground</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Transition transform -->\n<div class=\"transition-transform duration-300\"\u003eTransform</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Transition all properties -->\n<div class=\"transition-all duration-300\"\u003eAll Properties</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Duration\n\n```html\n<!-- Duration options -->\n<button class=\"transition duration-75\"\u003e75ms</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-100\"\u003e100ms</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-150\"\u003e150ms</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-200\"\u003e200ms</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-300\"\u003e300ms (default)</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-500\"\u003e500ms</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-700\"\u003e700ms</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition duration-1000\"\u003e1000ms</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Easing (Timing Functions)\n\n```html\n<!-- Ease options -->\n<button class=\"transition ease-linear\"\u003eLinear</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition ease-in\"\u003eEase In</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition ease-out\"\u003eEase Out</button\u003e\n<button class=\"transition ease-in-out\"\u003eEase In Out (default)</button\u003e\n```\n\n## Transform Utilities\n\n### Scale\n\n```html\n<!-- Scale up on hover -->\n<div class=\"transform transition hover:scale-110 duration-300\"\u003e\n  Scale 110%\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Scale down on hover -->\n<div class=\"transform transition hover:scale-95 duration-300\"\u003e\n  Scale 95%\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Card with scale effect -->\n<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300\"\u003e\n  Hover to scale\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Rotate\n\n```html\n<!-- Rotate on hover -->\n<button class=\"transform transition hover:rotate-45 duration-300\"\u003e\n  Rotate 45°\n</button\u003e\n\n<!-- Continuous rotation -->\n<div class=\"animate-spin h-8 w-8 border-4 border-blue-500 border-t-transparent rounded-full\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n<!-- Chevron icon rotation -->\n<button class=\"group\"\u003e\n  <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transform transition group-hover:rotate-180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n    <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" /\u003e\n  </svg\u003e\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Translate\n\n```html\n<!-- Move up on hover -->\n<div class=\"transform transition hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300\"\u003e\n  Move up\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Move right on hover -->\n<div class=\"transform transition hover:translate-x-2 duration-300\"\u003e\n  Move right\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Button with arrow animation -->\n<button class=\"group flex items-center space-x-2\"\u003e\n  <span\u003eLearn More</span\u003e\n  <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 transform transition group-hover:translate-x-1\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n    <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\" /\u003e\n  </svg\u003e\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n## Built-in Animations\n\n### Spin\n\nFor loading indicators:\n\n```html\n<!-- Simple spinner -->\n<div class=\"animate-spin h-8 w-8 border-4 border-blue-500 rounded-full border-t-transparent\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n<!-- Button with spinner -->\n<button class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded\" disabled\u003e\n  <svg class=\"animate-spin h-5 w-5 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n    <circle class=\"opacity-25\" cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\"\u003e\u003c/circle\u003e\n    <path class=\"opacity-75\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4zm2 5.291A7.962 7.962 0 014 12H0c0 3.042 1.135 5.824 3 7.938l3-2.647z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\n  </svg\u003e\n  <span\u003eLoading...</span\u003e\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Pulse\n\nFor skeleton loading states:\n\n```html\n<!-- Skeleton card -->\n<div class=\"max-w-sm rounded overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-white p-6\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"animate-pulse flex space-x-4\"\u003e\n    <div class=\"rounded-full bg-gray-300 h-12 w-12\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    <div class=\"flex-1 space-y-4 py-1\"\u003e\n      <div class=\"h-4 bg-gray-300 rounded w-3/4\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n      <div class=\"space-y-2\"\u003e\n        <div class=\"h-4 bg-gray-300 rounded\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        <div class=\"h-4 bg-gray-300 rounded w-5/6\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n      </div\u003e\n    </div\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Bounce\n\nFor attention indicators:\n\n```html\n<!-- Notification dot -->\n<div class=\"relative inline-block\"\u003e\n  <span class=\"absolute -top-1 -right-1 flex h-3 w-3\"\u003e\n    <span class=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-red-400 opacity-75\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n    <span class=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-red-500\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  </span\u003e\n  <button class=\"p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded\"\u003e\n    <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n      <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9\" /\u003e\n    </svg\u003e\n  </button\u003e\n</div\u003e\n\n<!-- Scroll down indicator -->\n<div class=\"animate-bounce\"\u003e\n  <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\n    <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3\" /\u003e\n  </svg\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Common Patterns\n\n### Hover Card Lift\n\n```html\n<div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 transform transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg duration-300\"\u003e\n  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\"\u003eCard Title</h3\u003e\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600\"\u003eCard content...</p\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Button Press Effect\n\n```html\n<button class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded transform transition active:scale-95 hover:bg-blue-600\"\u003e\n  Click Me\n</button\u003e\n```\n\n### Image Zoom on Hover\n\n```html\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"\u003e\n  <img\n    src=\"image.jpg\"\n    alt=\"Zoomable\"\n    class=\"transform transition hover:scale-110 duration-500\"\n  />\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Fade In Overlay\n\n```html\n<div class=\"relative group\"\u003e\n  <img src=\"image.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"w-full\" />\n  <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-center justify-center\"\u003e\n    <span class=\"text-white font-bold\"\u003eView Project</span\u003e\n  </div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n### Staggered Animation\n\n```html\n<div class=\"space-y-2\"\u003e\n  <div class=\"opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_0.5s_ease-in_forwards]\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.1s\"\u003eItem 1</div\u003e\n  <div class=\"opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_0.5s_ease-in_forwards]\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.2s\"\u003eItem 2</div\u003e\n  <div class=\"opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_0.5s_ease-in_forwards]\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.3s\"\u003eItem 3</div\u003e\n</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Custom Animations\n\nYou can add custom animations in your Tailwind config:\n\n```javascript\n// tailwind.config.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  theme: {\n    extend: {\n      animation: {\n        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.5s ease-in',\n        'slide-in': 'slideIn 0.5s ease-out',\n      },\n      keyframes: {\n        fadeIn: {\n          '0%': { opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideIn: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\nUsage:\n```html\n<div class=\"animate-fade-in\"\u003eFades in</div\u003e\n<div class=\"animate-slide-in\"\u003eSlides in</div\u003e\n```\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n```html\n<!-- Transitions -->\nclass=\"transition duration-300 ease-in-out\"\n\n<!-- Transform on hover -->\nclass=\"transform transition hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1\"\n\n<!-- Built-in animations -->\nclass=\"animate-spin\"      <!-- Continuous rotation -->\nclass=\"animate-pulse\"     <!-- Fade in/out -->\nclass=\"animate-bounce\"    <!-- Up/down bounce -->\nclass=\"animate-ping\"      <!-- Scale out fade -->\n```\n\n**Remember:**\n- ✅ Use `transition` with `duration` for smooth changes\n- ✅ Use `transform` before scale/rotate/translate utilities\n- ✅ Use built-in animations for common patterns\n- ✅ Use `ease-in-out` for most transitions\n- ✅ Consider `prefers-reduced-motion` for accessibility\n- ❌ Don't animate expensive properties (width, height, top, left)\n- ❌ Don't forget to add `transform` class before transform utilities",
